acution:
1.set the dell notebook as following:
     secure mode is off
     uefi mode is off 
     legacy mode is on.
2.partioning :
     It is just set the /boot partioning
     it must not set the /boot/efi partioning

3. the 3th partion (/boot) is fat32 or vfat format which use for the /boot partioning.

4. the 3th partion (/boot) need mark to the "boot" tag. 
